# Nikolsk, Mukhorshibirsky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Nikolsk () is a rural locality (a selo) in Mukhorshibirsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 1,309 as of 2010. There are 20 streets.
Geography
Nikolsk is located 45&nbsp;km northeast of Mukhorshibir (the district's administrative centre) by road. Khonkholoy is the nearest rural locality.
